\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}
}{}$G_{\text{post}}$\end{document}. In both networks, the majority of nodes have just a few neighbours; for example, 65% of the nodes in \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym}
\usepackage{amsfonts}
\usepackage{amssymb}
\usepackage{amsbsy}
\usepackage{upgreek}
\usepackage{mathrsfs}
